      <title>拜登盟友在周末疯狂竞选中拒绝辞职呼吁</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-30/biden-loyalists-dismiss-calls-to-quit-in-frenetic-weekend-blitz</link>
